{"lastModified":1763452468078,"uri":"c::7819198761::vessel::d5cccd15-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Italy\n\nAlalunga 78 flybridge Arma VII: an elegant motoryacht available for one of the most picturesque cruises in the Mediterranean. Tasteful and refined interiors, modern, fast and luxurious, the yacht offers accommodation for up to 8 guests in four wonderful cabins located on the lower deck. Both the master and the VIP suite are full-beam, this means they’re very spacious, light and airy. Two twin cabins offer an additional pullman bed. On the main deck, a beautiful salon offers ample space to relax on two sofas and a separate formal dining area. On the foredeck a spacious and perfectly equipped galley allows our chef to cook delicious meals. Alalunga 78 flybridge also boasts expansive deck space: on the aft deck there is a beautiful alfresco dining area while on the foredeck a beautiful solarium is ideal for sunbathing. The fly bridge features a large sun-pad and a dinette. With her polished interiors, her ample deck spaces and her top speed, she will safely and comfortably transport her guests for incredible journeys at the discovery of the breathtaking Mediterranean coasts.\n","blueprint":{"name":"ARMA VII","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd15-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3249c180-3d5e-11f0-b712-7bc67ff254db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd15-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c7eebc50-3d5d-11f0-b712-7bc67ff254db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd15-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c7dbd090-3d5d-11f0-b712-7bc67ff254db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd15-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c7eb60f0-3d5d-11f0-b712-7bc67ff254db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd15-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c7db8270-3d5d-11f0-b712-7bc67ff254db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd15-fe8c-